headline: Prologis (PLD) Valuation Check After 27% Share Price Gain Over the Past Year
summary: Prologis (PLD) has quietly outperformed the wider real estate sector this year, and with the stock up about 27% over the past year, investors are asking whether the current price still makes sense. See our latest analysis for Prologis. That move has been powered less by short term excitement and more by steady confidence, with the 90 day share price return of 11.49 percent feeding into a 12 month total shareholder return of 26.88 percent.
